# Azure AD Credentials
# Get these from https://portal.azure.com

# Your Azure Application (Client) ID
# Found in: App registrations → Your app → Overview
AZURE_CLIENT_ID=b19296ae-5d39-445b-8f4b-397b13e2d85a

# Your Azure Client Secret
# Found in: App registrations → Your app → Certificates & secrets
# ⚠️ Keep this PRIVATE - never commit to git
AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=58f64947-2ae2-4e88-86eb-bb0bf34d93a4

# Your Azure Directory (Tenant) ID
# Found in: App registrations → Your app → Overview
AZURE_TENANT_ID=02bfaf98-142b-4cf3-b8b8-27cde0b9adf3

# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local (in your GitHub repo root)
# 2. Replace the x's with your actual values from Azure
# 3. Do NOT commit .env.local to git
# 4. In Vercel dashboard, add these as environment variables:
#    - Settings → Environment Variables
#    - Paste each value from .env.local
# 5. Vercel will use these when deploying
#
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
